data.description: ** Fantastic Price Improvement Below Market Value !! Great Buy !! Don't Miss !! **Spectacular Floorplan In Popular Villages at Olde Point. This Beautiful Home Is Conveniently Located Near The Beach, Shopping, Dining, Parks, Boating & A Short Drive To Wilmington. Recent Upgrades Include New HVAC 2023, New Hardwood Stairs & Smart Home Thermostats. Interior Painted. The Entire Yard Was Regraded & New Sod (Zoysia) Was Planted. Large Living Room W/ Gas Log Fireplace. Gourmet Kitchen W/ Granite Counter Tops, Deluxe Staggered-Height Cabinets, Large Center Island & Stainless Steel Appliances. First Floor Office/ Bedroom. Spacious Master Bedroom With Sitting Area & Oversized Walk-In Closet. Secondary Bedrooms Have Walk-In Closets. Open Bonus Room/ Loft. Private Patio Overlooks Beautiful Landscaped Fenced Back Yard With Custom Firepit Patio, Great For Entertaining. **
